                  <a href="http://www.usdoj.gov/atr/public/guidelines/ncrpa.htm">http://www.usdoj.gov/atr/public/guidelines/ncrpa.htm </a></p>
              <p align="left"> <span class="style2"><em> The ANSI policies and procedures referred to above may be found and downloaded <a href="http://public.ansi.org/ansionline/Documents/Standards%20Activities/American%20National%20Standards/Procedures,%20Guides,%20and%20Forms/">here</a>. </em></span></p>
              <p align="left"><span class="style2"><em> For more on best practices on forming and participating in SSOs, see: The Essential Guide to Standard Setting and Consortia: <br>
              </em><a href="/essentialguide/">http://www.consortiuminfo.org/essentialguide/
              </a></span> </p>
